PerfectPlan (“the App”) is a simple, offline task-management application designed to help users manage to-dos, notes, shopping lists, reminders, and other personal tasks.
This Privacy Policy explains how the App handles user data. By using the App, you agree to the terms described below.

1. No Personal Data Collection

PerfectPlan does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.

Specifically, the App does not collect:

Name, email, phone number

Contacts

Calendar data

Location information

Device identifiers

Advertising identifiers (GAID/IDFA)

Usage analytics

Cookies or tracking information

All data created in the App stays entirely on your device.

2. Offline Operation

PerfectPlan works completely offline.

The App does not connect to any server.

No data is uploaded, synced, or shared over the internet.

No external accounts or sign-ins are required.

3. Local Storage Only

All tasks, notes, reminders, and app preferences are stored locally on your device.
The data remains under your full control, and uninstalling the App will delete all locally stored data.

PerfectPlan does not have access to your data and cannot retrieve any data after deletion.

4. No Third-Party Services

PerfectPlan does not integrate any third-party SDKs, including:

Analytics SDKs

Advertising SDKs

Tracking SDKs

Cloud services

Social media integrations

There are no advertisements, no tracking, and no background data transfers.

5. Permissions

PerfectPlan uses only minimal, device-local permissions (if any).
These permissions are used solely for app functionality and never to collect or transmit data.

The App does not request sensitive permissions such as location, contacts, microphone, or camera.

6. Children’s Privacy

PerfectPlan does not collect any personal information from children or adults.
The App is safe for users of all ages because no data is collected.

7. Open-Source Notice

PerfectPlan is based on open-source components licensed under the MIT License.
The App may include modifications to MIT-licensed code, but all privacy-related behavior remains the same:
no data is collected, shared, or transmitted.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated in the future.
If changes are made, the updated version will be available within the app or on the distribution page.

9. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the App, you can contact the developer at:

Email: j68392555@gmail.com
